	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Obiit <persName type="auto_name">Bustan</persName> bascia legatis 40m coronatorum pro redimendis, qui capti fuerant ad <persName type="auto_name">Gerbas</persName> propterea, quod aiebat tamdiu pestem Bizantii sęvituram, quamdiu detinerentur.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Miliones septem apud eum reperti cesserunt <persName type="auto_name">Solimano</persName>, et Eli bascia, natione <persName type="auto_name">Sclavus</persName>, ei suffectus est.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dux <placeName type="auto_name">Sessę</placeName> propediem <placeName ref="l306" cert="high">Mediolanum</placeName> redibit cum uxore.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Papa Bononiam</persName> cogitat; pro papa erit Puteus cardinalis.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Inter nepotes papales non admodum convenit, quum <placeName type="auto_name">Itali</placeName> videant sibi praeferri <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l822" cert="high">Germanos</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Agitur de sorore <persName type="auto_name">Philippi</persName> iungenda <placeName ref="l150" cert="high">Ferrariensi</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Subditi a <placeName ref="l1098" cert="high">Florentino</placeName> exiguntur 300m coronatorum.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name">Dux Albanus</persName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l834" cert="high">Italiam</placeName> repetet cum <persName type="auto_name">Ioanne Austriaco Senarum</persName> principe designando.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Munitur <placeName type="auto_name">Bergomum</placeName> vel potius desolatur civibus frustra deprecantibus.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Omnia geruntur consilio et autoritate <persName type="auto_name">Sfortie Palavicini</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note>[Zusätze von <persName ref="p495" type="auto_name">Bullingers</persName> Hand:]</note>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Es söllend 28 schiff mitt kriegsvolck uß <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispanua</placeName> zuͦ <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1121" cert="high">Ianua</placeName> ankummen sin.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Die <placeName type="citizen_name">3 Länder</placeName><note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Uri, Schwyz und Unterwalden (vgl. <bibl>SI</bibl> III 1298).</note> schrybend den 3 Pündten, sy söllend die predicanten uß dem <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l323">Mousaxer</placeName> taal thuͦn, oder one rächt wöllend sy inen das nitt nachlassen; dann sy in gfar, das ouch die iren anstössen verfürt.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Dorumb ist ein tag gen <placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Chur</placeName> angesähen 28. augusti.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sic isti homines omnibus tandem praescribunt, non tantum <placeName ref="l646" cert="high">Claronensibus</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="date">[Datum, Unterschrift und Adresse fehlen]</note>
				</p>
			</div>
